description: BitScapes Season 2. The one and only Ordinals banner collection!This fine art is perfectly sized to be presented across your social media accounts and accompany your PFPs.This collection consists of:104 black and white BitScapes.50 golden BitScapes.21 Bitcoin memento collage BitScapes.The 21 Bitcoin memento collage BitScapes consists of all the 154 "BitScapes Season 2" placed together to form one collage banner presenting an art piece with a visible Bitcoin logo.
